Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se Description

The EPP defines different services or commands that must be mapped to and from Java objects. Each SendSE class has a corresponding XML representation which is an EPP service element that should be sent from the client to the server. Each ReceiveSE class should be given the appropriate type of XML document, which is an EPP service element received by the client from the server, from which the object will make available the data in the service element.
